and, avait 23 ans. Il a épousé Agnes De Blakeland en 1285, à Calne, Wiltshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé en 1286, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 21 ans, et a été enterré à Calne, Wiltshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni."},"de":{"1265–1286":"1265–1286","1270–1365":"1270–1365","1286–1366":"1286–1366","1242–1286":"1242–1286","1242–1303":"1242–1303","1259":"1259","1303":"1303","1366":"1366","1365":"1365","1265":"1265","1286":"1286","1242":"1242","1285":"1285","1270":"1270","Calne, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom":"Calne, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom","Calne, Wiltshire Unitary Authority, Wiltshire, England":"Calne, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom","Calne, Calne, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom":"Calne, Wiltshire, England","Calne, Wiltshire, England":"Calne, Wiltshire, England","Blakeland, Calne, Wiltshire, England":"Calne, Wiltshire, England","lifeSummary":"Als Robert De Blakeland VI 1265 in Calne, Wiltshire, England geboren wurde, war sein Vater Sir Robert de Blakeland V 23 und seine Mutter Lady Agnes Buckland 23. Er hat 1285 in Calne, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom Agnes De Blakeland geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Sohn. Er starb 1286 im Alter von 21 Jahren in seinem Geburtsort und wurde in Calne, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom begraben."},"ht":{"1265–1286":"1265–1286","1270–1365":"1270–1365","1286–1366":"1286–1366","1242–1286":"1242–1286","1242–1303":"1242–1303","1259":"1259","1303":"1303","1366":"1366","1365":"1365","1265":"1265","1286":"1286","1242":"1242","1285":"1285","1270":"1270","Calne, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom":"Calne, Wiltshire, Angletè, United Kingdom","Calne, Wiltshire Unitary Authority, Wiltshire, England":"Calne, Wiltshire, Angletè, United Kingdom","Calne, Calne, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom":"Calne, Wiltshire, England","Calne, Wiltshire, England":"Calne, Wiltshire, England","Blakeland, Calne, Wiltshire, England":"Calne, Wiltshire, England"},"hu":{"1265–1286":"1265–1286","127